      • changeAnnotationValue

        public static Object changeAnnotationValue(Annotation annotation,
                           String key,
                           Object newValue)
        Changes the annotation value for the given key of the given annotation to newValue and returns the previous value. Modified from http://stackoverflow.com/a/28118436
        Parameters:
        annotation - the QueryFile annotation applied to the test method
        key - a String equal to "list"
        newValue - a String containing a comma-separated list of test files
        Returns:
        the old value of the annotation, which should be an empty String array
